 <description translatable="no">
	<p>Features:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>EcotubeHQ can output hardware accelerated h.264, h.265, vp9 and av1 codecs.</li>
        <li>EcoTubeHQ offers two video upscaling methods: 'Quality' and 'Powersave'. 'Quality' uses
AMD FidelityFX Super Resolution to enhance video quality, ‘Powersave’ is aimed at increasing
the battery life of laptops.</li>
        <li>EcoTubeHQ restricts 720p videos to 30fps to minimize data requirements.</li>
        <li>EcoTubeHQ offers debanding to enhance video quality.</li>
        <li>EcoTubeHQ automatically opens low resolution YouTube videos [144p / 240p] in a small
window which can be used as a low bitrate miniplayer.</li>
        <li>EcoTubeHQ offers drag and drop video playlists.</li>
        <li>EcoTubeHQ can play local video files with AMD FidelityFX Super Resolution.</li>
        <li>EcoTubeHQ offers two Opus audio bitrates for av1 and vp9 YouTube videos - 70kbps and
160kbps.</li>
      </ul>
 </description>
